<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蟲子這東西啊，<delay20 />
隔著這距離看<delay8 />剛剛好。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是靠得太近，<delay8 />你可別後悔啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們的樣子不只是超出想像，<delay8 />
有時候會長得很奇特啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蟲子這東西，<delay8 />
真是不可小覷啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />
這房間裡的蟲子離我們有點遠，<delay20 />
你也能放心看啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />走在這房間裡，<delay20 />
我就會忍不住擔心，<delay8 />要是蟲子停在
我的頭上或肩膀上該怎麼辦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡讓我想起
小時候<delay8 />老爸帶我去露營過啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那時蟲子跑進帳篷裡，<delay frames="30" />
完全不肯出去。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那時可真夠慘的啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不知道蟲子會在什麼時候<delay8 />
從什麼地方跑出來。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可別太大意喔？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過這地方還真像極樂世界啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
蝴蝶看起來<delay8 />就像來迎接我們。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開玩笑的啦，<delay20 />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不過，<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />只要在這房裡看到蟲子，<delay frames="40" />
不好了，<delay20 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會哈欠打不停<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hot" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡<delay8 />真是危機蟲蟲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開～玩笑的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡沒那麼危險啦，<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得好像有很多雙眼睛<delay8 />
盯著我們啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />原來是蟲子在看我們啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">是喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />這麼說你喜歡蟲囉？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我嗎？<delay frames="30" />我<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
不、<delay20 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管哪種蟲我都沒問題喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡的蟲子們怎麼樣？<delay8 />很壯觀吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這裡的蟲不能抓，<delay20 />
但你可以慢慢看喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧了<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />讓我一年四季
都能觀賞到各種昆蟲！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這理想<delay8 />可能沒辦法馬上達成，<delay20 />
不過哪天<delay8 />我還真想看看
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />島上抓得到的所有昆蟲咧，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我們島上的<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />才剛蓋好沒多久，
昆蟲的數量還很少，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺裡頭空蕩蕩的啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過要是等這裡都充滿昆蟲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來一定<delay20 />超有魄力的啦！
你不覺得嗎！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要是能在這裡揮捕蟲網，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是個練習捕蟲的好機會了啊。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！</message>
</msbt>